text.tspan: Cereal is not a good person, but he's so bad at his job
that he isn't really dangerous, and he just turns out
to seem funny. See, he's a serial killer. Note the
stereotypical apron and plaid shirt. But ever since he
got his head replaced with a music box — voluntarily,
might I add — he hasn't been able to see anything at
all. You can tell he didn't think the music box idea
through at all. He also changed his name from
whatever it was before to "Cereal." I think he meant to
say "serial," but whatever. Just don't say you aren't
dead, and he probably won't try to kill you.
He sucks at his job (and spelling)
Alignment: Evil (but he sucks at it)
